Source: gfxboot
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Stefan Lippers-Hollmann <s.l-h@gmx.de>
Build-Depends: cdbs, debhelper (>= 5.0.0), patchutils, dpatch, x-dev, libx11-dev, nasm, xmlto
Standards-Version: 3.7.2

Package: gfxboot
Architecture: amd64 i386
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Recommends: grub-gfxboot (>> 0.97-5)
Suggests: gfxboot-theme-suse | gfxboot-theme-sles | gfxboot-theme-nld
Description: bootlogo creator for gfxboot compliant boot loaders
 This package is needed to create the graphical boot logos for gfxboot, 
 introduced and developed by SuSE, it is suitable for grub, lilo and syslinux.

Package: gfxboot-theme-suse
Architecture: all
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, gfxboot (>> 3.2)
Description: SuSE theme for gfxboot-compliant boot loaders
 This package places the source for the SuSE gfxboot theme under 
 /usr/share/gfxboot-theme-suse/.

Package: gfxboot-theme-sles
Architecture: all
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, gfxboot (>> 3.2)
Description: SLES theme for gfxboot-compliant boot loaders
 This package places the source for the SuSE SLES gfxboot theme under 
 /usr/share/gfxboot-theme-sles/.

Package: gfxboot-theme-nld
Architecture: all
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, gfxboot (>> 3.2)
Description: NLD theme for gfxboot-compliant boot loaders
 This package places the source for the Novell Linux Desktop (NLD) gfxboot 
 theme under /usr/share/gfxboot-theme-nld/.

Package: gfxboot-theme-zen
Architecture: all
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, gfxboot (>> 3.2)
Description: Zen theme for gfxboot-compliant boot loaders
 This package places the source for the SuSE Zen gfxboot theme under 
 /usr/share/gfxboot-theme-nld/.

